column2: BRIEF-Tsakos Energy Navigation Announces New Charter For Product Tanker And Sale Of Oldest Vlcc April 26 (Reuters) - Tsakos Energy Navigation Ltd: * TEN, LTD. ANNOUNCES NEW CHARTER FOR PRODUCT TANKER AND SALE OF OLDEST VLCC * TEN LTD - FIXTURE OF MR EXPECTED TO GENERATE ABOUT $10.0 MILLION OF GROSS REVENUES OVER EXTENDED DURATION OF CONTRACT * TEN LTD - SALE OF VLCC WILL GENERATE $7.5 MILLION OF FREE CASH AFTER REPAYMENT OF APPLICABLE DEBT Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
